item.description:
@adamknightz wrote:

There is none, but in the file that records commands used, they used ::sit and ::unsit before a bunch of times. :eek:

I checked another DSPK, and there isn’t a sit command in there either. I’m not 100% sure it was a DSPK though, it never actually said it was a DSPK, but comments said it was.

Do you know any DSPK server? I can’t seem to find one.
